title: Bryce Courtenay - 03 Solomons Song
description: When Mary Abacus dies, she leaves her business empire in the hands of the warring Solomon family. Hawk Solomon is determined to bring together both sides of the tribe - but it is the new generation who must fight to change the future. Solomons are pitted against Solomons as the families are locked in a bitter struggle that crosses battlefields and continents to reach a powerful conclusion. SOLOMON&#039;S SONG is a novel of courage and betrayal in which Bryce Courtenay tells the story of Australia&#039;s journey to nationhood.
